decks.notes: The key concept of this Selesnya Aggro deck is to quickly and efficiently establish a strong board presence with low-cost creatures like Elvish Mystic and Llanowar Elves. The deck utilizes the combo potential of Collected Company to dig for additional creatures and gain value from the enter-the-battlefield abilities of cards like Skyclave Apparition and Bishop of Wings. The deck aims to deal damage early and often, leveraging the lifelink and angel synergies provided by Resplendent Angel and Righteous Valkyrie. The deck also includes some utility lands like Boseiju, Who Endures and Eiganjo, Seat of the Empire, as well as a few high-impact creatures like Sigarda, Font of Blessings.
